{"tid":1367982,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"727@振興元朗嘉年華@即將開始。各類活動小總結","createTime":"2019-07-26T11:35:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T11:57:23.000Z","uid":9049,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"094d42c94ece47ea7dfe72f930ee3f8d2fe5b347","tid":1367982,"uid":9049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T11:35:22.000Z","msg":"活動種類繁多，各位得閒就入黎玩下啦！<br />\n<br />\n緊記注意安全，小心扒手！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">何韻詩簽名會</span></span><br />\n有機會野生捕獲HOCC<br />\n獲得合照及親筆簽名<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5yqyseR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5yqyseR.png&h=1c3e4f55&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Pokemon GO 特殊挑戰</span></span><br />\n日日鍛練去取勝<br />\n機會黎啦，係玩朗捕捉超夢夢！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KHEfFHq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKHEfFHq.png&h=4799e971&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">國際老婆餅日</span></span><br />\n記住買齊老婆餅、老公餅同水先好入去<br />\n不要幫襯無良小販<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UbHMNnY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUbHMNnY.png&h=902c660d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n尋找傳說中嘅<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">世外桃源</span></span><br />\n花海在等你<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GyZO0JJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGyZO0JJ.png&h=39d81d5b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">行街街 X 郊遊</span></span>都好正家！<br />\n帶齊裝備免受傷，注意小童安全<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U8WqivG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU8WqivG.png&h=2cad47d5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pcb52Xn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fpcb52Xn.png&h=8cccaf38&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後送上元朗天書<br />\n就萬無一失啦！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yaoL2X6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyaoL2X6.png&h=dfc560d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>遊玩人士請注意⚠️以下事項：<br />\n1. 入夜後極危險，所有活動必須在太陽下山前完結<br />\n2. 進入村落有機會被拉入暗角打鑊<br />\n3. 建議組隊<br />\n4. Press and camera are our friends<br />\n5. 真狗/假狗同樣會咬人<br />\n6. 緊就逃生路線<br />\n7. Be Water</strong></span>"},{"pid":"29b1ea184d37ed6a4ac082dffc66d1da14f11994","tid":1367982,"uid":36761,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T11:37:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/m64n5cK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fm64n5cK.jpg&h=434be3bb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"62f9092c83dd03393a73205b4d68f77ddb53f98c","tid":1367982,"uid":9049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T11:57:23.000Z","msg":"推比多d人知"}]}